extends layout

block content
  h2 NOGALSS Registration Token
  p Hello #{name},
  p Thank you for your payment. Here is your secret, one-time registration token for the NOGALSS Cooperative Platform:
  h3(style="background: #f0fdf4; padding: 15px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 24px; color: #008A62; border: 2px dashed #008A62; letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 25px 0;") #{token}
  p Please keep this code safe. Copy it and use it on the member registration page to securely finalize your profile creation.
  p If you did not initialize this payment, please contact support immediately.
